							"text": "FAIRO: Fairness-Aware Sequential Decision Making for Human-in-the-Loop CPS",
							"articleLocation": "pdfs/ICCPS2024-1FkhQC4Dfn57pDzqp6O87q/692700a087/692700a087.pdf",
