							"text": "LLMSense: Harnessing LLMs for High-level Reasoning Over Spatiotemporal Sensor Traces",
							"articleLocation": "pdfs/SenSys-ML2024-289uwd0h4TYiUQIAEKhdK1/633600a009/633600a009.pdf",
