							"text": "A Hybrid Approach to WCTT Analysis in a Real-Time Switched Ethernet Network",
							"articleLocation": "pdfs/RTAS2024-2YY4oP4nFEPkTHWM9dDUYo/584100a161/584100a161.pdf",
