							"text": "NaviSlim: Adaptive Context-Aware Navigation and Sensing via Dynamic Slimmable Networks",
							"articleLocation": "pdfs/IoTDI2024-45xciEppCNCyxkOl1ds1Qh/702500a110/702500a110.pdf",
