							"text": "Poster Abstract: Towards a Predictive Model for Improved Placement of Solar-Powered Urban Sensing Nodes",
							"articleLocation": "pdfs/IoTDI2024-45xciEppCNCyxkOl1ds1Qh/702500a215/702500a215.pdf",
